{"tid":2052093,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【日本真男神】伊勢谷友介六四撐港 ：我也支持香港市民","createTime":"2020-06-05T09:06:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T20:13:05.000Z","uid":37554,"like":57,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"aaea32d88085ada8cdfbd02b74ff4142ee51c76e","tid":2052093,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T09:06:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200605/SNAAX73M4QQXSOV4IZIM3GK5DI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200605%2FSNAAX73M4QQXSOV4IZIM3GK5DI%2F&d=hYhEKVoQeS8%2B2u2S5aPGGZuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=978d81c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200605%2FSNAAX73M4QQXSOV4IZIM3GK5DI%2F&h=721ec006\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200605/SNAAX73M4QQXSOV4IZIM3GK5DI/</a><br />\n<br />\n圈中型男伊勢谷友介趁昨日六四，在Twitter轉發朝日電視台新聞女主播長野智子的留言，並貼出英國首相約翰遜談到會向香港人伸出友誼支持之手的新聞，伊勢谷友介更親自留言：「我也支持香港市民！在現代，政府的連貫政策使社會變得倒退。日本也經歷這個問題。維吾爾族和西藏正在遭受苦難。」最後更加＃香港加油＃維吾爾＃西藏，相當有心。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Iseya_Yusuke/status/1268334533251747840\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIseya_Yusuke%2Fstatus%2F1268334533251747840&d=hYhEKVoQeS8%2B2u2S5aPGGZuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=12b0b24c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIseya_Yusuke%2Fstatus%2F1268334533251747840&h=493cac96\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Iseya_Yusuke/status/1268334533251747840</a>"},{"pid":"655dce303c8db8ebd676b53eff016d89d9930deb","tid":2052093,"uid":104035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T16:40:34.000Z","msg":"入去retweet"},{"pid":"5fa5eab83e319669a2af285712f7f7a0db998ee4","tid":2052093,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T16:46:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bef3d60b9af5208fbeadac5264df88ac5ed0b6e","tid":2052093,"uid":24739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T16:57:28.000Z","msg":"男神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3e1902234b652e30e360152d6a0a657bad3b2a8","tid":2052093,"uid":18120,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T18:44:11.000Z","msg":"嗱，又一例子，心地好樣咪好囉，你睇香港啲垃圾奶共偽人，個個騎呢怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f42962c7b1789bdd5f327629d8820897ba7cb5db","tid":2052093,"uid":157064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T18:45:17.000Z","msg":"等睇粉紅玻璃心碎"},{"pid":"d624b35a141879aaebfb9c2c7496f325a08983a2","tid":2052093,"uid":150675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T18:48:19.000Z","msg":"新宿天鵝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eb7f83c862ba40846ba586edb8be9b83822e4f0","tid":2052093,"uid":31744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T19:01:23.000Z","msg":"「假分手」掩人耳目 長澤雅美、伊勢谷友介遭爆愛玩SM<br />\n<br />\n女星長澤雅美與男友伊勢谷友介交往1年多，原本有望步入禮堂，日前卻驚爆因價值觀落差大吵分手，更遭雜誌踢爆她曾懷孕，擔心影響工作而私下墮胎，幕前形象大打折扣，如今再傳她頻頻與對方透過視訊傳情，「假分手」只為掩人耳目。<br />\n<br />\n原本長澤雅美和伊勢谷友介交往穩定，但根據《周刊實話》報導，一位與經紀公司交情不錯的知情人士爆料，事務所以「對事業不利」為由強迫分開，表面上看似分手，實際上兩人常靠視訊或私會延續感情，但躲躲藏藏讓她壓力大增，瀕臨爆炸階段，才會做出挑逗合作男星伊澤英明的怪異舉動。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">該周刊加碼爆料伊勢谷友介個性為S型，而長澤雅美屬於M型，都享受和情人之間的「暴力」互動，她似乎也私下和朋友透露無法忘懷兩人的「閨房」樂趣</span>，種種勁爆言論恐怕再度影響她的演藝名聲。<br />\n<br />\n(來源：NOWnews)"},{"pid":"b344f6c4f0408d5e3cb4b1a805e8575a85b33312","tid":2052093,"uid":105924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T20:08:33.000Z","msg":"好想畀伊勢谷友抱住黎屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfc36bfbb1b931307fc1b6fa62cdcf02bcb8ccd9","tid":2052093,"uid":299372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T20:13:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}